msgstr "より簡潔にすると::"

#: ../../source/changelog.rst:169
msgid ""
"The ``multiple`` groups may now be anonymous, and should from now on be defined with the ``multiple`` keyword placed in lieu of "
"the group name. This makes their behavior more consistent and easier to understand. The behavior of named multiple groups is "
"unchanged, but they should not be used going forward."
