"There have been several changes to the `default_focus` property of focusable displayables like buttons and bars. This property "
"allows Ren'Py to select a displayable to gain default focus when displayables are added to removed."
msgstr ""
"ボタンやバーのようなフォーカス可能な Displayable の `default_focus` プロパティーにいくつかの変更があります。このプロパティーは "
